title: The Townhall Weekend Journal for NOV-15-2013 FRI
description:
The Townhall Weekend Journal for NOV-15-2013 FRI




Friday, November 15, 2013


Obamacare shatters to pieces



Weekend Journal



Hugh Hewitt speaks with Senators Marco Rubio and Ron Johnson 
   about the failed Obamacare roll out 
     and why its hurting so many Americans.

 Michael Medved and Dennis Prager look at President Obama's apology
    about you being able to keep your plan.

 Michael Medved interviews an author who claims that interfaith families
    are a great idea. 

 Bill Bennett chats with Michael Rubin about Iran's pursuit of a nuclear weapon.

 Medved closes with a few words of insight from Lady Gaga. 
       
            Yes, Lady Gaga.
